  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5190353/" class="title-link">败军之殇</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5190353"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48823429/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48823429-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48823429/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">林</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-11-28"
      class="main-meta">2011-11-28 22:46:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5190353_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一个英雄的部队，一段传奇的历史，我读这本书是因为想了解为什么这支在民族独立战争中所做出贡献，在内战中又全军覆灭？被损的一无是处？可是读过之后我觉得作者想象的成分太多，要是作为史料就有点勉强！还是对这置部队的历史不算太清晰。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5190353/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
